'''Urbo Zirtran''' was one of the [[Zirtran brothers (disambiguation)|Zirtran brothers]] who purchased the ''[[KV-29233-44B]]'' prototype and sold it to the [[Geelan]], who converted it into the [[Space station/Legends|space station]] later to be known as [[Zirtran's Anchor/Legends|''Zirtran's Anchor'']].<ref name="Zirtran's Anchor (article)">{{JournalCite|5|Zirtran's Anchor (article)}}</ref>

